title: Crypto is going to get regulated...
description:
Crypto vs. Congress -- it's about time these boomers started regulating crypto. Whether you're pro or anti crypto, either way it's good that our lawmakers are setting the guidelines for how innovation can proceed. The wild west needs to calm down so that people can suffer fewer scams and enjoy more stable markets with crypto.
